court: IN THE HIGH COURT OF JUDICATURE AT BOMBAY ORDINARY ORIGINAL CIVIL JURISDICTION NOTICE OF MOTION 2334 OF 2005 IN CONTEMPT PETITION NO. 170 OF 1999 IN SUIT NO. 38 OF 1978 The New India Assurance Co.
